# Rule: Markdown files are pure content. No frontmatter.

## Forbidden
- Do NOT create YAML frontmatter (--- ... ---) in any .md file.
- Do NOT store IDs, tags, status, routing, or any metadata inside markdown.

## Enforcement
- If a markdown file contains frontmatter, you MUST:
  1) Remove the entire frontmatter block
  2) Ensure "<file>.meta.yaml" exists and is updated via tools/osmeta.py
